 and beast; I will consume the fowls of the heaven, and the fishes of the sea, and the stumblingblocks with the wicked; and I will cut off man from off the land, saith the LORD.","year":-630},{"id":"rec0MCs5H6Xu1uq09","ref":"Zeph.1.4","text":"I will also stretch out mine hand upon Judah, and upon all the inhabitants of Jerusalem; and I will cut off the remnant of Baal from this place, and the name of the Chemarims with the priests;","year":-630},{"id":"recXlOV8P6deVtWfA","ref":"Zeph.1.5","text":"And them that worship the host of heaven upon the housetops; and them that worship and that swear by the LORD, and that swear by Malcham;","year":-630},{"id":"rec31C3RoMWE2mQJB","ref":"Zeph.1.6","text":"And them that are turned back from the LORD; and those that have not sought the LORD, nor enquired for him.","year":-630}]}
